<p>Who was in charge of the Sumerian (said) "You spoke. . .," caned me.<br />
My teacher (said) "Your hand is not good," caned me.<br />
I neglected the scribal art, [I forsook] the scribal art,<br />
My teacher did not. . .,<br />
